fields.name: Kinky Coily Clip-in Hair Extensions
fields.description:
Introducing the enhanced BYE BYE Leave-Out™ Glam Set Clip-Ins. A single bundle provides ample coverage for a full head of hair. Featuring innovative invisible root mimicking technology for an undetectable look, these clip-ins offer a seamless blend near your parting, requiring minimal to no leave-out. This user-friendly product is perfect for beginners.

Hair Specification: 11 Pieces,32 clips
Two wefts with 5 clips
Two wefts with 4 clips
Two wefts with 3 clips
One weft with 2 clips
Two BYE BYE leave-out™ wefts With 2 clips
Two BYE BYE leave-out™ wefts with 1 clip

Pre-Sale, Processing Time: 20-25 business days
Attention: When creating kinky and coily clips, we choose kinky texture hair for the BYE BYE leave-out™ wefts.

fields.name: Cooper Brown Curly Wig
fields.description:
For Mannequin Pic:
Hair Texture: Coily & Curly
Hair Length: 16 Inches
Hair Weight: 160g
Wig Type: Half Wig, Machine-made Weft


Her Story:
It's a wig but not just one wig! Compared with traditional half wigs, with this unique cap construction, this unit can be comfortably placed anywhere, unlocking limitless styling options and being friendly to beginners! This wig could be styled as a headband wig, half wig, or drawstring ponytail. Maybe you can find more styles with this wig! # glueless wig #halfwig # 3in1 #3 in 1 #multi textured

Processing Time:
10-15 business days.
